Image:Aimee Teegarden by David Shankbone.jpg|thumb|Aimee Teegarden 2008
Aimee Richelle Teegarden (born October 10, 1989) is an American actress and model. She played Jenny Randall in the 2011 movie "Scream 4". She modeled for campaigns including Old Navy, Tommy Hilfiger and Hollister. She was born in Downey, California.
